This is the code repo for the work presented in "Topological Assessment of Recoverability in Metro Networks" (Renzo Massobrio and Oded Cats).

Contact info:
Renzo Massobrio
R.M.Massobrio@tudelft.nl

======
Set-up:

1. Create the conda environment with the dependencies: "conda env create -f environment.yml"
2. Download experimental results from here: https://surfdrive.surf.nl/files/index.php/s/NWoDdfPk5OyK1rM
3. Place the files in the "exps" directory

======
Run:

1. Open a terminal in this directory
2. Activate the environment: "conda activate recoverability" 
3. Run "jupyter notebook"
